'''Koffi Gahou''' (22 Ukwakira 1947 - 24 Kanama 2019) yari umuhanzi, umukinnyi wa filime, n'umuyobozi<ref>Koffi Gahou - Person profile on Africultures <nowiki>http://africultures.com</nowiki> › people</ref>.

== Ubuzima ==
Gahou yavukiye i Cotonou ku ya 22 Ukwakira 1947. Yize kuva 1986 kugeza 1989 mu kigo cy’ubushakashatsi bw’ikinamico muri Kaminuza ya Sorbonne Nouvelle Paris 3<ref>Black notebook:The artist Koffi Gahou is no more - Benin <nowiki>https://actubenin.com</nowiki> › carnet-noirlar...</ref>, abona uruhushya rwo kwigisha. Kuva mu 1985 kugeza 1986 Gahou yakoraga umwuga wo kwimenyereza  muri Conservatoire national supérieur d'art ikinamico i Paris maze mu 1988, yimenyereza umwuga muri Institut international de la marionnette<ref>Benin: The cultural world mourns Koffi Gahou - Matin Libre <nowiki>https://matinlibre.com</nowiki> › ... › Culture</ref>.  Guhera mu 1974, yize ubwe mu buhanzi bwa plastiki, imashini zometse ku rukuta, amashusho, ndetse n’imbere<ref>Koffi Gahou — Google Arts & Culture</ref>. Gahou yinjiye mu bakozi ba Leta nk'umuhanzi kandi akora ibitaramo mu itsinda rya "Cerveaux noirs". Yashinze kandi itsinda ry’ikinamico "Zama Hara"<ref>Koffi Gahou - Arts-bahamas <nowiki>http://bahamas.spla.pro</nowiki> › file.person.koffi-gahou.6107.html</ref>, yagize imurikagurisha ryinshi ry’ibikorwa bye muri [[Afurika]], [[Uburayi]], Cuba, na [[Amerika]].<ref>Bénin : Le monde culturel pleure Koffi Gahou - Matin Libre <nowiki>https://matinlibre.com</nowiki> › ... › Culture</ref> 

Gahou yakoze imyenda "Yovo Helou e, Akowe helou e" mu 1990. Irerekana imbata zifatanije amaboko inyuma, kandi byari byiza cyane<ref>L'artiste béninois Koffi Gahou a tiré sa révérence <nowiki>http://easy.africahotnews.com</nowiki> › ...</ref>. Mu 2000, Gahou yakinnye murumuna wa Boubacar, umuhinzi, muri film ya Jean Odoutan ''Barbecue Pejo''<ref>Qu'est-ce Koffie. Encyclopédie (what-this.com)</ref> . 

Mu mashusho ya videwo muri Mata 2019, Gahou yasabye ko yishyurwa miliyoni 30 z’amafaranga CFA y’umudepite wo muri Bénine yategetswe kumuha n’Urugereko rwa 3 rw’ubucuruzi rw’urukiko rwa Cotonou<ref>Mots clés: Benin - Page 6 sur 23 - Journal d'Afrique - JA <nowiki>https://www.journaldafrique.com</nowiki> › tag</ref>. Iki kibazo cyaturutse mu marushanwa yo mu 2007 Gahou yatsinze ariko ntiyabona amafaranga yigihembo. <ref>Benin - World Encyclopedia of Puppetry Arts | UNIMA <nowiki>https://wepa.unima.org</nowiki> › benin</ref>Gahou yapfuye ku ya 24 Kanama 2019 i Abomey . Umuhango wo kumushyingura wabaye ku ya 25 Nzeri<ref>Search for "Claire Houngbo" - FilmAffinity</ref>. 
